>>> traefik/
>>>
>>> docker/
>>>
>>> system/
>>>
>>>
>>> Logs are invaluable when diagnosing:
>>> certificate failures
>>> DNS issues
>>> container crashes
>>> routing problems
>>> Rotate logs regularly so they don't consume excessive disk space.
>>> 4.14 Health Checks
>>> Every service should expose a health endpoint where possible.
>>> Docker can periodically test whether a service is responsive.
>>>
>>> If a health check fails repeatedly, Docker can restart the container
>>> automatically.
>>>
>>> This is one of the easiest ways to improve long-term reliability.
